{"tid":1299204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李奠的目的好清晰","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:16:19.000Z","uid":40902,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00a37370623f2690e80967c3a8edefd04fcfe160","tid":1299204,"uid":40902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:10:21.000Z","msg":"佢用呢隻字就係想外國媒體翻譯做<br />\nthe bill is dead<br />\n外國文宣應該要澄清番呢個唔係法律用詞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n唔好俾佢地以為爭取成功<br />\n</span> 仲要show俾佢地睇政府開始裝cctv 三年內落實信用評級 同李家超條仆街大大聲話要參考新疆<br />\n<br />\n今次輸左香港就正式玩完 唔可以好似雨革後做番港豬<br />\n大家要堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11191e4e0ddb50365e4c9fbcd3aef77cdf29b2b","tid":1299204,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人如果唔想你下一代無得做人而只係一堆分數既<br />\n今次反送中 我地一定要贏盡， 一分都唔可以讓<br />\n認真， 唔係香港實玩完， 咁點解我地唔搏盡<br />\n仲有唔好犧牲自己 每一個人既力量都好重要<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人一定要反對「社會信用體系」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298408</a></span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"405626ac28348fbc3b08d6c25c88ab1d78b31ba8","tid":1299204,"uid":139474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:10:44.000Z","msg":"又玩字眼屌佢<br />\n<br />\n[一圖睇哂]警隊大撚哂 保安局部隊化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"143e9c787ddead68fac0279144c7e05d0ce9eb05","tid":1299204,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1eaa512c1c5d6f874e691fb109249c262ab51ffd","tid":1299204,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:11:00.0